data.description: CREDIT TOWARDS a MOVING TRUCK!  BRING AN OFFER! Stunning 3 bedroom (potential 4th), 3 full bathrooms The PERFECT place to call home. MASTER ON MAIN w/Ensuite. Beautiful MTN & RIVER VIEWS from the spacious living room. Hardwoods flow throughout the main level as well. LARGE OPEN KITCHEN w/CHEF'S PANTRY! French doors lead to a large deck off the main level boasting a soothing, luxurious HOT TUB - perfect to soak your evening away. Spacious Den w/Cozy Fireplace and FULL WET BAR. Game room with it's own separate dining area. A separate room can be utilized as an office, study, library or a 4th bedroom. Work bench & Extra Storage. MULTI CAR FULLY COVERED CARPORT w/room for a boats, a motorhome, a motorcycle, or ATV recreational vehicles. This home welcomes you to its large, level, and professionally landscaped lot. HOME WARRANTY INCLUDED! Annual City Fireworks Visible from the privacy of Your Own Yard!!! Community boasts a PARK, relaxing paved WALKING PATH, and local TENNIS COURTS, and PUBLIC BOAT/RIVER DOCK ACCESS. Bring your boat and enjoy the beauty this community has to offer!
